1. Decide where to order pizza from.
1a. Ask yourself how much money you want to spend.
1b. Decide on a pizza establishment that aligns with budget.
2. Look up menu from pizza establishment.
2a. Ignore all the healthy options.
3. Decide what pizza to order.
3a. Consider wings.
4. Call the pizza establishment.
5. Order the desired pizza.
6. Pay over the phone.
7. Wait for the pizza to arrive.
7a. Tip the driver.
8. Enjoy the pizza.